OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTeachers' racist WhatsApp  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchat caught by pupils      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Israel's education minister has        
OL,6, apologised to Ethiopian Israeli        
OL,7, schoolgirls whose teachers mocked them 
OL,8, in a WhatsApp group on a school trip.  
OL,10,FThe girls spotted the teachers         
OL,11,Fmessaging each other in a chat group   
OL,12,Fthey created called Black School Trip. 
OL,14,FOne of the girls filmed the chat over a
OL,15,Fteacher's shoulder, then shared it on  
OL,16,Fsocial media, calling the teachers "a  
OL,17,Fdisgrace".                             
OL,19,FThe teachers involved were suspended   
OL,20,Fand the incident is being investigated.
